WiFi & BT Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with the popular **Realtek RTL8821CS WiFi/BT module** which supports BT/BLE 2.1/3.0/4.2, as well as 802.11ac/abgn 433Mbps 2.4/5.8 GHz Wireless LAN (WLAN).

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A55/Others/WiFi_BT.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *RTL8821CS WiFi/BT Module*

The |product| includes an SMA connector for an external WiFi/BT antenna, as illustrated in the figure below.

.. rst-class:: text-center

   |wifi_bt_img|

   *WiFi+BT Antenna SMA*
